(121, 39, 'product', 'CĂN HỘ CAO CẤP', '{\"brief\":{\"vi\":\"N\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a ng\\u00f4i nh\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1eadp trung xung quanh m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0nh lang trung t\\u00e2m l\\u1edbn \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 l\\u00e0 l\\u1ed1i \\u0111i ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a giao th\\u00f4ng v\\u00e0 khu v\\u1ef1c l\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c ph\\u00f2ng li\\u1ec1n k\\u1ec1. H\\u00e0nh lang ch\\u1ea3y v\\u00e0o m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ea7u thang l\\u1edbn, r\\u1ed9ng, cung c\\u1ea5p ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n ch\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i ra ngo\\u00e0i.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u1ede ph\\u00eda nam c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ed9i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0 ph\\u00f2ng kh\\u00e1ch l\\u1edbn ph\\u00eda tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc. Ph\\u00f2ng n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 gi\\u1ea5y d\\u00e1n t\\u01b0\\u1eddng g\\u1ed1c bao g\\u1ed3m c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea5m tr\\u1ea7n c\\u00f3 h\\u00ecnh nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00fa chim nh\\u1ecf v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng b\\u00f4ng hoa m\\u00e0u cam v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc l\\u00e1 m\\u00e0u xanh l\\u00e1 c\\u00e2y v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng r\\u1ef1c r\\u1ee1 tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n m\\u00e0u xanh lam nh\\u1ea1t. Ph\\u1ea7n ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a h\\u00ecnh n\\u1ec1n l\\u00e0 s\\u1eafc th\\u00e1i.\"},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"<font style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#555555; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:start; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; vertical-align:inherit\\\">H\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1eb7t b\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00e1ng l\\u1ec7 n\\u00e0y l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea7u danh s\\u00e1ch c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n ngay t\\u1eeb khi b\\u1ea1n b\\u01b0\\u1edbc qua h\\u00e0ng hi\\u00ean b\\u1eb1ng g\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o v\\u00e0o s\\u00e2n trong theo phong c\\u00e1ch Tuscan v\\u1edbi B\\u1ee9c tranh t\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0 khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn th\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ee9ng. g\\u1ed7 s\\u1ed3i, t\\u1ee7 k\\u00ednh v\\u00e1t c\\u1ea1nh, m\\u1eb7t b\\u00e0n b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00e1 c\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea1ch b\\u00f3ng lo\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 t\\u1ee7 b\\u1ebfp ri\\u00eang bi\\u1ec7t *C\\u1eeda x\\u1ebfp k\\u00e9p m\\u1edf ra kho\\u1ea3ng s\\u00e2n tr\\u00e0n ng\\u1eadp \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng *Ph\\u00f2ng kh\\u00e1ch trang nh\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 c\\u1ea3 m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ea3 xu\\u1ed1ng cho r\\u1ea1p h\\u00e1t t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 *Ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1ee7 d\\u00e0nh cho kh\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0 l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng Xuy\\u00ean su\\u1ed1t dinh th\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u00e1ng kinh ng\\u1ea1c n\\u00e0y b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1t c\\u00e1c t\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u.&nbsp;<\\/font><font style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#555555; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:start; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; vertical-align:inherit\\\">C\\u1eeda v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ee5 ki\\u1ec7n t\\u1eeb Ph\\u00e1p, c\\u1eeda s\\u1ed5 k\\u00ednh m\\u00e0u t\\u1eeb Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u.&nbsp;<\\/font><font style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#555555; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:start; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; vertical-align:inherit\\\">H\\u1ea7m r\\u01b0\\u1ee3u d\\u01b0\\u1edbi g\\u1ea7m c\\u1ea7u thang.&nbsp;<\\/font><font style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#555555; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-wei